ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS by updating the definition of non-toxic shot to include tungsten-iron-nickel-copper shot as an approved alternative, by making minor adjusments to the existing definitions and by ensuring that the definition is consistent in all wildlife regulations.
